data.description: Spacious 4 bed, 2 bath home nestled in a quiet neighborhood with no HOA on the South end of Myrtle Beach.  Come see this move-in ready, turnkey home and enjoy the sunken living room with a double sided fireplace that can be enjoyed from both the living room and the fully enclosed Carolina room.  Your backyard is a private oasis; fully fenced and bordering a tranquil creek. Spend your days lounging on your private deck overlooking the creek, relaxing in the above ground pool or grilling under the covered back porch.
